description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions


Kate and Leisha discuss what they did for Thanksgiving and what documentaries they recommended to each other. They then give advice about moving to a different state and what embarrasses them.


Get Tickets To Their Live Show:
